of blowing
each other's brains out.

34
00:03:15,500 --> 00:03:17,333
Yes, of course I do,

35
00:03:17,416 --> 00:03:20,083
and I'd like you to stand by
while I put it into action.

36
00:03:20,166 --> 00:03:21,250
In three days,

37
00:03:21,333 --> 00:03:23,083
I'll have the ringleader
smoked out.

38
00:03:23,166 --> 00:03:25,041
Then you can do
what you will with them.

39
