a counter snipe?

42
00:03:38,500 --> 00:03:39,416
That's right.

43
00:03:39,500 --> 00:03:40,708
I don't know.

44
00:03:40,791 --> 00:03:42,875
Day after tomorrow,
the Godos will be invited

45
00:03:42,958 --> 00:03:45,291
to a meeting
of Inferno's senior members.

46
00:03:45,375 --> 00:03:47,250
