00:12:57,875 --> 00:13:00,333
Maybe in a place
where it sticks out?

264
00:13:00,416 --> 00:13:01,708
That's how we roll.

265
00:13:58,041 --> 00:13:58,750
Hey, Cal.

266
00:14:00,250 --> 00:14:02,500
Hey!
Oh, sorry.

267
00:14:02,583 --> 00:14:04,291
I didn't find anything yet.

268
00:14:04,375 --> 00:14:05,416
Yeah, me, neither.

269
00:14:05,500 --> 00:14:07,416
Well, on we go.

270
00:14:18,375 --> 00:14:20,500
Alright,
that's it for today.

271
00:14:20,583 --> 00:14:21,625
Hey, hold on.

272
00:14:23,083 --> 00:14:24,000
Look!

273
00:14:24,083 --> 00:14:25,791
This place seems
a little weird.

274
00:14:25,875 --> 00:14:27,958
How so?

275
00:14:28,041 --> 00:14:28,750
Check it out.

276
00:14:39,416 --> 00:14:41,166
Good catch!
Nice one.

277
00:14:41,250 --> 00:14:42,208
I got it?

278
00:14:42,291 --> 00:14:43,041
You did.

279
00:14:56,916 --> 00:14:58,375
Yeah, this is it alright.

280
00:14:58,458 --> 00:14:59,916
Our sniper's gonna be
right there.

281
00:15:01,541 --> 00:15:03,125
Okay.

282
00:15:03,208 --> 00:15:04,666
So I guess you're gonna
wanna be here

283
00:15:04,750 --> 00:15:07,041
to get a good shot at him.

284
00:15:07,125 --> 00:15:08,250
Yeah.

285
00:15:08,333 --> 00:15:10,166
Is he the one?

286
00:15:10,250 --> 00:15:13,333
You think he's the one
who killed Judy?

287
00:15:13,416 --> 00:15:14,458
I don't know.

288
00:15:14,541 --> 00:15:15,500
Probably.

289
00:15:16,833 --> 00:15:17,916
I'd at least
be willing to bet

290
00:15:18,000 --> 00:15:20,625
he's
one of the people responsible.

291
00:15:20,708 --> 00:15:22,750
I wanna be with you
when it happens.

292
00:15:25,250 --> 00:15:26,625
Please let me see it.

293
00:15:26,708 --> 00:15:29,041
I want to see you shoot
this guy in the head!

294
00:15:29,125 --> 00:15:31,208
You shouldn't
want to see that, Cal,

295
00:15:31,291 --> 00:15:32,375
no one should.

296
00:15:35,500 --> 00:15:37,791
I saw Judy.

297
00:15:37,875 --> 00:15:39,833
It happened
right in front of me.

298
00:15:39,916 --> 00:15:41,625
Nobody asked me
if I wanted to see it,

299
00:15:41,708 --> 00:15:43,541
but I had to watch her die.

300
00:15:46,333 --> 00:15:49,125
Sometimes, a sniping mission
will be assigned to two people

301
00:15:49,208 --> 00:15:51,333
that are working together.

302
00:15:51,416 --> 00:15:52,791
Like a team.

303
00:15:52,875 --> 00:15:54,916
Some say a sniper
needs an assistant.

304
00:15:58,416 --> 00:16:00,000
The assistant will spot,

305
00:16:00,083 --> 00:16:01,916
their job is to keep an eye
on the target

306
00:16:02,000 --> 00:16:03,666
and the surroundings.

307
00:16:03,750 --> 00:16:05,791
It helps the sniper
stay focused.

308
00:16:05,875 --> 00:16:08,125
They're like an observer.

309
00:16:08,208 --> 00:16:10,166
They watch,
but they don't shoot.

310
00:16:12,375 --> 00:16:14,125
Can you do that?

311
00:16:14,208 --> 00:16:15,166
Yes!

312
00:16:16,750 --> 00:16:18,791
All right,
give me your hand.

313
00:16:20,291 --> 00:16:21,250
What for?

314
00:16:23,500 --> 00:16:24,916
Your payment for today.

315
00:16:30,416 --> 00:16:31,625
Oh, wow!

316
00:16:34,333 --> 00:16:35,916
Ohmigod, thank you!

317
00:16:38,375 --> 00:16:40,666
I'll take good care of it.

318
00:16:40,750 --> 00:16:43,916
I promise I will, always.

319
00:17:09,000 --> 00:17:12,083
That's where he's gonna be,
the sun'll be behind us.

320
00:17:12,166 --> 00:17:14,750
So he shouldn't
be able to see us.

321
00:17:14,833 --> 00:17:16,375
That's the plan at least.

322
00:17:36,291 --> 00:17:37,208
It's time.

323
00:17:37,291 --> 00:17:39,083
Isaac and his guys
just got here.

324
00:17:39,166 --> 00:17:40,708
Good.

325
00:17:40,791 --> 00:17:43,333
Funny thing is,
Randy Weber's M.I.A.

326
00:17:43,416 --> 00:17:45,333
Seems a little
suspicious to me.

327
00:17:45,416 --> 00:17:46,500
This is a pretty big deal,

328
00:17:46,583 --> 00:17:47,833
so why wouldn't he bring
his right hand man

329
00:17:47,916 --> 00:17:49,791
along with him?

330
00:17:49,875 --> 00:17:51,541
You think they're gonna
try to pull something?

331
00:17:57,041 --> 00:17:58,541
Today's the big day.

332
00:17:58,625 --> 00:17:59,916
I can't wait to see

333
00:18:00,000 --> 00:18:02,333
what that woman
is gonna pull out of her ass.

334
00:18:02,416 --> 00:18:03,916
How do I look, boys?

335
00:18:04,000 --> 00:18:05,958
A stunning white suit
and a loaded gun.

336
00:18:06,041 --> 00:18:07,916
Seems appropriate
for jumping into hell.

337
00:18:09,125 --> 00:18:10,500
Let's go, Shiga.

338
00:18:10,583 --> 00:18:12,041
Yes, sir.

339
00:18:12,125 --> 00:18:14,833
Wherever you go, you can
count on me to follow you there.

340
00:18:17,416 --> 00:18:19,708
I don't see anyone
over there, Reiji.

341
00:18:19,791 --> 00:18:22,291
Do you think he could maybe
be hiding someplace else?

342
00:18:22,375 --> 00:18:24,625
Just relax, it's early.

343
00:18:48,375 --> 00:18:51,333
Welcome, sirs, to Inferno.

344
00:18:52,791 --> 00:18:54,541
It's him!

345
00:18:54,625 --> 00:18:57,166
He's behind the water tower!

346
00:18:57,250 --> 00:18:58,500
I see him.

347
00:18:58,583 --> 00:18:59,916
What about a face?

348
00:19:00,000 --> 00:19:01,541
Can you see his face?

349
00:19:01,625 --> 00:19:02,875
All I see is the gun.

350
00:19:02,958 --> 00:19:04,958
I can't even tell
if it's a man or a woman.

351
00:19:14,416 --> 00:19:15,541
This is bad, Reiji!

352
00:19:15,625 --> 00:19:18,333
He's about to fire!
Hurry!

353
00:19:18,416 --> 00:19:19,541
No way!

354
00:19:21,291 --> 00:19:23,666
It can't be her.

355
00:19:23,750 --> 00:19:24,875
What's wrong?

356
00:19:24,958 --> 00:19:26,708
I know what I did.

357
00:19:26,791 --> 00:19:27,791
She's dead!

358
00:19:29,333 --> 00:19:30,416
She's dead!

359
00:19:30,500 --> 00:19:31,750
I killed her!

360
00:19:34,458 --> 00:19:35,500
Eren!

361
00:19:35,583 --> 00:19:38,583
Come on! Shoot him!

362
00:19:38,666 --> 00:19:39,916
Show yourself!

363
00:19:40,000 --> 00:19:41,083
Reiji?

364
00:19:41,166 --> 00:19:42,750
Show me your face!

365
00:19:46,083 --> 00:19:46,791
Get him!

366
00:20:02,500 --> 00:20:03,458
No!

367
00:20:06,541 --> 00:20:08,416
Ohmigod, Reiji,
are you okay?

368
00:20:08,500 --> 00:20:09,500
Did he get you?

369
00:20:11,375 --> 00:20:12,666
I'm fine!

370
00:20:12,750 --> 00:20:14,583
It's just a scratch.

371
00:20:18,500 --> 00:20:20,291
You're so stupid.

372
00:20:20,375 --> 00:20:22,833
Why would you
do something so stupid?

373
00:20:26,375 --> 00:20:27,875
Couldn't help it.

374
00:20:27,958 --> 00:20:30,250
Chalk it up to some kinda
morbid curiosity.

375
00:20:32,708 --> 00:20:34,041
You did a good job today.

376
00:20:34,125 --> 00:20:34,833
I'm proud of you.

377
00:20:37,458 --> 00:20:40,666
Come on, Cal,
you got revenge for Judy.

378
00:20:40,750 --> 00:20:42,500
That's a big deal.

379
00:20:42,583 --> 00:20:43,541
Yeah.

380
00:20:44,916 --> 00:20:46,333
Listen...

381
00:20:46,416 --> 00:20:49,166
we know who's been pulling
the strings this whole time.

382
00:20:49,250 --> 00:20:50,416
It's over.

383
00:21:14,750 --> 00:21:16,333
I can't believe
you bastards!

384
00:21:17,791 --> 00:21:19,583
What the heck just happened?

385
00:21:19,666 --> 00:21:22,041
The one we got wasn't alone.

386
00:21:22,125 --> 00:21:22,958
What?

387
00:21:25,916 --> 00:21:26,916
Can't be!

388
00:21:28,250 --> 00:21:29,583
No way.

389
00:21:41,708 --> 00:21:45,333
Mission accomplished.

390
00:21:45,416 --> 00:21:46,541
No way!

391
00:22:00,083 --> 00:22:01,541
Yes...

392
00:22:01,625 --> 00:22:02,625
Master.

393
00:22:06,458 --> 00:22:09,458
[Music]

394
00:23:40,166 --> 00:23:41,833
I can't live without him.

395
00:23:41,916 --> 00:23:43,875
I wanna be with him forever.

396
00:23:43,958 --> 00:23:45,458
I'll try so hard.

397
00:23:45,541 --> 00:23:46,791
I'll do whatever I have to

398
00:23:46,875 --> 00:23:49,333
to make him feel
the same way about me.

